ves him two days and then comes again on the fourth day"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "counting the day of the next preceding fit as the first;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "having,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "seized by, a quartan fever"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "murobaEN", "text_ar": "مُرْبَعٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, K;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "murobiEN", "text_ar": "مُرْبِعٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is said to be used in the same sense; but the Arabs say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "murobaEN", "text_ar": "مُرْبَعٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (Az, TA.)       -A3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aroDN marobuwEapF", "text_ar": "اَرْضٌ مَرْبُوعَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$ajarN marobuwEN", "text_ar": "شَجَرٌ مَرْبُوعٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Land,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "trees, watered by the rain in the season called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rabiyE", "text_ar": "رَبِيع"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "marobuwEN", "text_ar": "مَرْبُوعٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", applied to a man, also signifies (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Restored from a state of poverty to wealth"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "competence"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sufficiency; recovered from his embarassment"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "difficulty,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from a state of perdition"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "destruction."}, {"kind":